The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT) and focuses on economic aspects of computer science (cs.EC). The paper also discusses algorithms and optimization (cs.DS), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques for pricing-based mechanisms.
